<subSubSection pageId="7" pageNumber="412" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="7.[151,1437,1487,1874]" pageId="7" pageNumber="412">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,315,1739,1765]" pageId="7" pageNumber="412">Remarks.</emphasis>
According to 
<bibRefCitation author="Pickard-Cambridge, O." box="[485,790,1739,1765]" pageId="7" pageNumber="412" pagination="112 - 129" refId="ref4926" refString="Pickard-Cambridge, O. (1873) On some new genera and species of Araneida. Proceedings of the Zoological Society of London, 41, 112 - 129, pls. XII-XIV." type="journal article" year="1873">Pickard-Cambridge (1873)</bibRefCitation>
the original series consisted of 
<specimenCount box="[1166,1256,1739,1765]" pageId="7" pageNumber="412" type="male">2 males</specimenCount>
and 
<specimenCount box="[1318,1433,1739,1765]" pageId="7" pageNumber="412" type="female">4 females</specimenCount>
. However, only one male and 
<specimenCount box="[480,588,1775,1801]" pageId="7" pageNumber="412" type="female">4 females</specimenCount>
were found in OUMNH. Series label and first description gives the locality as 
<collectingCountry box="[183,264,1811,1837]" name="Sri Lanka" pageId="7" pageNumber="412">Ceylon</collectingCountry>
(now 
<collectingCountry box="[337,453,1811,1838]" name="Sri Lanka" pageId="7" pageNumber="412">Sri Lanka</collectingCountry>
). The record of this species from 
<collectingCountry box="[835,893,1811,1837]" name="India" pageId="7" pageNumber="412">India</collectingCountry>
by 
<bibRefCitation author="Simon, E." box="[937,1093,1811,1838]" pageId="7" pageNumber="412" pagination="279 - 314" refId="ref5111" refString="Simon, E. (1906) Arachnides (2 e partie). In: Voyage de M. Maurice Maindron dans l'Inde meridionale. 8 e Memoire. Annales de la Societe Entomologique de France, 75, 279 - 314." type="journal article" year="1906">Simon (1906)</bibRefCitation>
cannot be confirmed. 
<bibRefCitation author="Roewer, C. F." pageId="7" pageNumber="412" refId="ref5012" refString="Roewer, C. F. (1955) Katalog der Araneae von 1758 bis 1940, bzw. 1954. Vol. 2. Institut Royal des Sciences naturelles de Belgique, Bruxelles, 923 pp." type="book" year="1955">Roewer (1955)</bibRefCitation>
and 
<bibRefCitation author="WSC" box="[280,425,1847,1873]" pageId="7" pageNumber="412" refId="ref5694" refString="WSC (2020) World Spider Catalog. Version 19.0. Natural History Museum, Bern. Available from: http: // wsc. nmbe. ch (accessed 29 April 2020)" type="url" year="2020">WSC (2020)</bibRefCitation>
, both list the 
<typeStatus box="[575,623,1848,1874]" pageId="7" pageNumber="412">type</typeStatus>
locality as 
<collectingCountry box="[752,813,1847,1873]" name="India" pageId="7" pageNumber="412">India</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
